55
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:28,510
Ale minulý rok umrela.

56
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,130
To ma mrzí.

57
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:33,410
Nech sa páči.

58
00:07:54,670 --> 00:07:56,100
