72
00:10:10,070 --> 00:10:12,800
Prešli ste kontrolou.

73
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:16,810
To je  skvelé!

74
00:10:17,210 --> 00:10:21,810
Prosím, toto vypíšte.

75
